column4: The right to view and/or download material without financial, registration, or excessive advertising barriers. [https://ceds.ed.gov/element/001561#FreeAccess]

The right to view and/or download material without financial barriers but users are required to register or experience some other low-barrier to use. [https://ceds.ed.gov/element/001561#FreeAccessWithRegistration]
Some material is available for viewing and/or downloading but most material tends to be accessible through other means. [https://ceds.ed.gov/element/001561#LimitedFreeAccess]
The right to view, keep, and/or download material upon payment of a one-time fee. [https://ceds.ed.gov/element/001561#AvailableForPurchase]

The right to view and/or download material, often for a set period of time, by way of a financial agreement between rights holders and authorized users. [https://ceds.ed.gov/element/001561#AvailableBySubscription]
Publisher defined conditions that govern the user's ability to access a learning resource.
